```{r setup, include=FALSE}

library(pander)
library(tidybayes)
library(brms)
library(magrittr)
library(pander)
library(tidybayes)
d <- read.csv("../datafiles/Raw_combined_excel.csv")
varlist <- unique(d$variety)


```


```{r}
i = 1

  load(paste0("../modelfits/",varlist[i],"_3p_updated"))
  fit.test %>%
  gather_samples(`b_alpha[1]`, b_beta, b_eta, `temp_Intercept[1]`, `temp_Intercept[2]`, `Ysat[1]`) %>% 
  mean_qi() %>%
  pander

```
